      "descriptions": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "Spring-Cloud-Platform has a missing authorization vulnerability: 未授权新增菜单污染全局权限定义. 攻击者可未授权写入全局权限定义来源。`PermissionService.getAllPermission()` 会把 `base_menu` 中所有菜单转换为全局 `PermissionInfo`，影响系统对资源权限的定义和匹配。",
          "supportingMedia": [
            {
              "base64": false,
              "type": "text/html",
              "value": "Spring-Cloud-Platform has a missing authorization vulnerability: 未授权新增菜单污染全局权限定义. 攻击者可未授权写入全局权限定义来源。`PermissionService.getAllPermission()` 会把 `base_menu` 中所有菜单转换为全局 `PermissionInfo`，影响系统对资源权限的定义和匹配。<p>This issue affects Spring-Cloud-Platform.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
